                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony2-rest/edit/master/knpu/episode1/delete-programmer.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>So you have to part ways with your programmer, and we all know goodbyes are hard.
So let's delete them instead. We're going to create an rm -rf endpoint to send a 
programmer to <code>/dev/null</code>.</p>
<p>Start with the test! <code>public function testDELETEProgrammer</code>, because we'll
send a DELETE request to terminate that programmer resource:</p>
