<p>Try the test and send a programmer to the trash! Filter for
<code>testDELETE</code>.</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">phpunit -c app --filter testPUTProgrammer</div></code></pre>
<p>Another endpoint bites the dust!</p>

    
